{"tid":1188397,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我媽是妓女我驕傲」　女大生不捨母親操勞被誤解","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T05:54:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f18c518eef75483b3da1dd8f9032813d9809403","tid":1188397,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"對於妓女這個行業，很多人不敢啟齒，不過英國一名18歲女大生瑪莉‧蘿絲(Marie Rose)，對於自己的38歲母親夏綠蒂‧蘿絲(Charlotte Rose)是妓女，完全不排斥，甚至大聲說：「我媽是妓女我驕傲。」<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，夏綠蒂從17歲開始就從事妓女行業，瑪莉說，她大約在12歲時，開始意識到媽媽的特殊職業。瑪莉承認一開始她也不敢告訴同學與老師，只說媽媽在從事電腦工作，她怕說出真相後，會被另眼對待。不過隨著年紀增長，瑪莉也越來越有勇氣承認母親的職業，甚至大力相挺，因為瑪莉自始至終都知道，母親是在做一份「對別人好」的職業。<br />\n<br />\n瑪莉回憶，由於母親職業的關係，常常晚歸甚至隔夜回家，但她可以體諒，甚至認為母親是她最佳的「性愛導師」，舉凡性事、男女關係，夏綠蒂都可以給出最佳建議。瑪莉也表示，她希望大家能稱呼她母親的職業為「應召女郎」，強調夏綠蒂不是一般的流鶯妓女，對於有些同學誤解為「AV女優」，她也感到失望。不過最讓瑪莉失望的，是完全無法正面接受妓女行業的人們，瑪莉說：「這份工作也是要努力賺錢，為何這些人不能理解這份職業，我為此感到非常沮喪。」<br />\n<br />\n夏綠蒂的收費標準為每小時160英鎊(約新台幣6400元)，她曾在2013年榮獲性工作者年度大賞，2016年更曾因協助裝上仿生陰莖的男子阿巴德(Mohammed Abad)破處，而成為新聞話題人物。不過瑪莉也說，夏綠蒂不只是為正常人服務的性工作者，她也經常幫助身障男女，讓他們重拾自我信心。<br />\n<br />\n至於瑪莉願不願意繼承夏綠蒂的職業，瑪莉坦言曾經想過，但她自認自己沒什麼耐心，所以後來決定作罷。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190606/640_40a86b07139e33e4767e22e8c5679edf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190606%2F640_40a86b07139e33e4767e22e8c5679edf.jpg&h=a82558ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190606/640_b895331bdbdbcee4f35f0a09a04b4af6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190606%2F640_b895331bdbdbcee4f35f0a09a04b4af6.jpg&h=3778c7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190606/640_cca4de6eb0ce7b2897b6ec0e85a4fd9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190606%2F640_cca4de6eb0ce7b2897b6ec0e85a4fd9c.jpg&h=f4c877b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190606/640_e650f7d9e7a116a289fe5ab4c5bfc125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190606%2F640_e650f7d9e7a116a289fe5ab4c5bfc125.jpg&h=81f4a9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190606/1579458/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190606%2F1579458%2F&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgoDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=40660d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190606%2F1579458%2F&h=4218924a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190606/1579458/</a>"},{"pid":"cded3123ba05acf2dc25c17bfe0b22a4f789d66b","tid":1188397,"uid":29080,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"女從母職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e856551b13a32e4dcc0d40041b6c84c4ee54360","tid":1188397,"uid":60814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"女承母業囉"},{"pid":"60ace19fe9e9955d7a00da7a26566f31ca46327c","tid":1188397,"uid":122134,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"每小時160英鎊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得咁支持呀媽做"},{"pid":"ae447e0c87637ea1f8665183164fd1181a7871dc","tid":1188397,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"個阿媽操到好横"},{"pid":"fed9f16cb7ac94fb29953af61a94912bc722007e","tid":1188397,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"夏綠蒂的收費標準為每小時160英鎊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h